OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely cloudy today with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of light rain at times,
OL,7,Fparticularly over the high ground. Low
OL,8,Fcloud will shroud the hills to give
OL,9,Fsome fog in the morning, but this will
OL,10,Fgradually lift. Winds strengthening in
OL,11,Fthe afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStaying cloudy tonight with
OL,14,Ffurther outbreaks of light and patchy
OL,15,Frain. A mild night across the region
OL,16,Funder the blanket of cloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
