OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAnother cloudy day with
OL,6,Ffurther outbreaks of rain. Rain will
OL,7,Fbe light at first, but may turn
OL,8,Fheavier across the north in the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA
OL,12,Fdrier start from next week with
OL,13,Fincreasing amounts of sunny spells.
OL,14,FStaying largely dry with warm sunshine
OL,15,Fand lighter winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
